Dennis Prager Radio Show


Prager 20140213  3 Brainwashed

Prager H3: Dennis talks to Sally Satel,
             resident scholar at AEI and Yale University lecturer
                and Scott Lilienfeld, professor of psychology at Emory University.

         Their new book is Brainwashed: The Seductive Appeal of Mindless Neuroscience

 Dennis builds on his interview to consider the question of whether addiction is
                a choice or a disease.

                Callers weigh in.




Prager 20140213  2 Married White

Prager H2: An Alabama legislator expresses anger at Supreme Court Justice,
              Clarence Thomas, because he married a white woman.
           
           The story sparks a spirited discussion with callers taking both sides of the issue.
